yield: per 2 carrots from a 1.5kg bag
ingredients:
  - item: carrots (equal size)
    qty: 2
    unit: ea
    basis: true
  - item: carrot juice
    note: from remaining carrots in bag
steps:
  - hold 2 roughly equal size carrots from a 1.5kg bag aside for cooking
  - juice remaining carrots and strain
  - cook carrots in juice (nearly covered) for 15-20 mins, until good texture
  - cook down remaining juice/stock
  - coat carrots in reduced stock
